        <object id="maplibre-boundary" label="&lt;b&gt;MAPLIBRE IS NOT A ROUTING ENGINE&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size:13px&quot;&gt;It receives already-calculated GeoJSON and renders it. It does not follow roads, calculate driving distance, produce ETA, or generate turn instructions.&lt;/font&gt;" petakerjaKey="routing-maplibre-boundary" labelEn="&lt;b&gt;MAPLIBRE IS NOT A ROUTING ENGINE&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size:13px&quot;&gt;It receives already-calculated GeoJSON and renders it. It does not follow roads, calculate driving distance, produce ETA, or generate turn instructions.&lt;/font&gt;" labelMs="&lt;b&gt;MAPLIBRE BUKAN ENJIN PENGHALAAN&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size:13px&quot;&gt;Ia menerima GeoJSON yang telah dikira lalu memaparkannya. Ia tidak mengekori jalan, mengira jarak pemanduan, menghasilkan ETA atau menjana arahan membelok.&lt;/font&gt;">
